01250ebcd6021d85","tid":1627933,"uid":89974,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:10:34.000Z","msg":"就咁睇落我係支持唔搞輕鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212978c71cc4dd73621c193d72e3a33cf5ccc9f1","tid":1627933,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:13:04.000Z","msg":"繼續討論"},{"pid":"4c983deef008be8cdfe711d8a100984dc755e5df","tid":1627933,"uid":162380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:13:59.000Z","msg":"咁都開到2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f440ebb679f6e1e8ef8cc4fb4e176405b580e1","tid":1627933,"uid":179689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:14:21.000Z","msg":"我要行唔緊要，我咩住full gear行4日山都係咁行<br />\n但我諗起區內既老人家就覺得好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋好多手足住屯碼/天水圍北無輕鐵你要佢地出黎<br />\n佢咩住gear行到已經身水身汗好攰<br />\n仲邊有力同你勇武，邊有力玩魔法<br />\n0成本唔拍卡要黨鐵義載<br />\n俾其他學生/有經濟困難既手足留返d錢買gear/支持黃店仲好<br />\n所以前線手足們，麻煩你地真係唔好搞輕鐵個信號<br />\n要佢無錢收咁繼續運作<br />\n搞拍卡機同增值已經好足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e990c273da5f4ad155bb52787b14f42d3f1e50ef","tid":1627933,"uid":15413,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:14:32.000Z","msg":"天北撚表示唔贊成搞輕鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de7167bf952504423c349b0377fe96279a64aea","tid":1627933,"uid":38131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e990c273da5f4ad155bb52787b14f42d3f1e50ef","tid":1627933,"uid":15413,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:14:32.000Z","msg":"天北撚表示唔贊成搞輕鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:15:41.000Z","msg":"住大西北既人今日真係濕撚滯<br />\n唔敢想像要返工返學日子"},{"pid":"6aad149e9af32e9b74fab05ba4f9d447a8a70c88","tid":1627933,"uid":259579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:16:02.000Z","msg":"唔好搞喇，返屋企訓覺啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講笑咋<br />\n一係叫佢搭的士啦，如果經濟上我可以支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果其他人屋企有同樣問題，我諗大家都會幫手，一齊諗辦法"},{"pid":"21c645bbc7f42d19f20a4c8d3b4098d4a521a390","tid":1627933,"uid":38131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aad149e9af32e9b74fab05ba4f9d447a8a70c88","tid":1627933,"uid":259579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:16:02.000Z","msg":"唔好搞喇，返屋企訓覺啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講笑咋<br />\n一係叫佢搭的士啦，如果經濟上我可以支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果其他人屋企有同樣問題，我諗大家都會幫手，一齊諗辦法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:16:48.000Z","msg":"的士都唔肯載喎你又知唔知呀<br />\n仲有你幫到幾多個?"},{"pid":"080d1d2a081265d0f8d106c3e08a58efcd89dd3a","tid":1627933,"uid":201414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:19:14.000Z","msg":"討乜鳩吖 成班自私撚 最好就快既爽既 咁講啱聽未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ff1d64fd23cc8bf9f2d49ff4eaf56fd70e5b9e","tid":1627933,"uid":259579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21c645bbc7f42d19f20a4c8d3b4098d4a521a390","tid":1627933,"uid":38131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aad149e9af32e9b74fab05ba4f9d447a8a70c88","tid":1627933,"uid":259579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:16:02.000Z","msg":"唔好搞喇，返屋企訓覺啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講笑咋<br />\n一係叫佢搭的士啦，如果經濟上我可以支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果其他人屋企有同樣問題，我諗大家都會幫手，一齊諗辦法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:16:48.000Z","msg":"的士都唔肯載喎你又知唔知呀<br />\n仲有你幫到幾多個?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:20:02.000Z","msg":"屌佢老人都唔載咁仆街 !?<br />\n想知上個POST 傾咗咁耐有冇大概共識 ?"},{"pid":"7e12e02eb6dadaeeedd05513e7275d746ea0e200","tid":1627933,"uid":